": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974836_1943374956076360_2484593514118294358_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8nKa8_-MD-oQ7kNvgGK0czb&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDmQ6l6EQKcyWRvj0K5WLkNve6dJn5DjsrTDKaARpWJCA&oe=676FF102"}, {"file_name": "1.png", "id": "445060168517426", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75462964_445060171850759_5520915542327767111_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MS8ArDhSiNEQ7kNvgGHBt-6&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBLGvxkKPLFEeAPs97Xc8-6WHjTG8TsPXpkia_1YOslGA&oe=676FDD84"}, {"file_name": "5.png", "id": "467916352871409", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003282_467916356204742_1871921057092171900_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YuQOpaQiFiAQ7kNvgHxlKgJ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBVt8M8OWzrfIt_8CTszC_3b1mLDrAIe2Dr0dGnIrTwVw&oe=676FFA62"}, {"file_name": "3.png", "id": "1934382610375855", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974473_1934382613709188_7156337812617042679_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=kR2lXPJNa4gQ7kNvgFd4qYi&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAu8-fO0WfwaLuTYzD3_9nVf9hxP3uBoty2ZvkUHXqwbQ&oe=676FE473"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "landscape.png", "id": "1524760081483769", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974531_1524760084817102_6497712644828891067_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wVe-C05YHrMQ7kNvgFfovPn&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBPEOCQU4uLriiWEQHOjQQQRmsou6HJBBRNOaRcqnhxtA&oe=676FE36F"}, "display_name": "Mystery Box VR: Hidden Secrets", "keywords": [], "long_description": " AN IMMERSIVE VR PUZZLE EXPERIENCE\nInteract with objects, handles, buttons, and wheels on each side. Crack enigmas and collect hidden puzzle tiles on a random side of the boxes.\n\nYou won't be able to compare reality with fiction.\n\n# DISCOVER INVENTIONS\nOnce you unlock all 8 boxes of a Level Pack, you can compose a puzzle and discover a brief history of an invention.\n\nIt's not always easy to escape the room, so use all your IQ to crack the riddles. There's a logic behind all of them, even where it seems it's not!\n\n# IMMERSIVE SOUNDTRACK\nPlay the game with your headphones to get immersed in this amazing adventure.\n\n# HINTS\nGot stuck on some enigma? No worries, you can still get a helpful hint! You can also get in touch with me in case you really can't make it through a riddle, I'll be glad to help ;)\n\n# MULTILANGUAGE\nAvailable in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.\n\nThe game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device", "short_description": "A VR escape room game where you have to solve intriguing riddles to open boxes and discover nice stories about popular inventions!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "$R36BSY5.png", "id": "3678762505771822", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031430_3678762509105155_2151975047074617165_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=y_iaIAWgr0wQ7kNvgEOQXaj&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBnme7FVrPoiS5DSg7iVdcAvsR_8FT7XSb6lhrc0DbdQA&oe=676FDF65"}, {"file_name": "$R81V725.png", "id": "2720695481426567", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75262743_2720695484759900_604086922326600035_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=j-hS5ssbrb0Q7kNvgGu1SfS&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCD4bmuy2caSkz17YqP7ecwIQnIfeyhL2XUq9ipcfBoNg&oe=676FDE4D"}, {"file_name": "$RQ3SN6U.png", "id": "1552311425628973", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982519_1552311428962306_1218130395049083834_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6